HEADWORD: Obcordate
<hw>Ob*cor"date</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>ob-</ets> + <ets>cordate</ets>.]</ety> <def>Heart-shaped, with the
